  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Drive Class 3 vehicles (van / light truck) as assigned by the company to collect parcels, store them at the required temperature, organize, and deliver to customers</li><li>Ensure the correct quantity and quality of goods are delivered safely and on time, minimizing damage and loss</li><li>Independently load and unload goods and hand over deliveries according to customer requirements</li><li>Assist the warehouse team with housekeeping and basic facility maintenance</li><li>Conduct daily vehicle inspections and cleaning; promptly report any vehicle faults or abnormalities</li><li>Comply with traffic regulations and company safety operating procedures</li><li>Perform any other ad-hoc duties as assigned by the supervisor</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 /4 driving license</li><li>Minimum 1 year of driving experience</li><li>Familiar with Singapore roads and traffic regulations; delivery experience is an advantage</li><li>Physically fit and able to perform loading and unloading duties</li><li>Careful, responsible, and detail-oriented</li><li>Good communication skills with a strong service mindset</li></ul>",
